milestones.description: This is the highest match aggregate (560) involving teams U.S.A. & U.A.E. in ODIs
Rohan Mustafa and Asif Khan's 105-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 100 between Shaiman Anwar and Rizwan
Netravalkar has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (41) for USA, going past Monank Patel
